(9, 2, '\n			<div>\n<p>在<a href="http://www.css3.info" target="_blank">CSS3 info</a>上看到这篇文章，很有用，拿来分享给各位国内的同学。</p>\n<p>这是一份近乎完整的<a title="CSS3动画-wordpress读者墙" href="http://www.daqianduan.com/css3-wordpress-wall/">CSS3</a>新增属性教学，视频是作者手把手教你如何使用CSS3这把利器。希望看完这些视频教学后你的CSS3水平有相当的提高。另外，如果你还有CSS3方面不懂得额地方，可以参看大前端的<a href="http://www.daqianduan.com/tag/css3%e8%af%a6%e8%a7%a3/">CSS3详解</a>，希望对你有帮助。</p>\n<h3>Borders</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/border-radius-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Border Radius: Part 1</a>?(5:46)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/border-radius-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Border Radius: Part 2</a>?(6:01)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/border-image-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Border Image: Part 1</a>?(6:13)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/border-image-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Border Image: Part 2</a>?(4:25)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/basic-box-shadows" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Basic Box Shadows</a>?(5:52)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/borders/advanced-box-shadows" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Advanced Box Shadows</a>?(5:19)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Gradients</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/gradients/linear-gradients-in-webkit" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Linear Gradients in WebKit</a>?(5:51)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/gradients/linear-gradients-in-firefox" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Linear Gradients in Firefox</a>?(2:33)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/gradients/radial-gradients-in-webkit" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Radial Gradients in WebKit</a>?(4:58)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/gradients/radial-gradients-in-firefox" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Radial Gradients in Firefox</a>?(3:46)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/gradients/additional-syntax" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Additional Syntax</a>?(4:56)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Animation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/transitions-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Transitions: Part 1</a>?(5:54)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/transitions-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Transitions: Part 2</a>?(6:28)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/2d-transforms-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">2D Transforms: Part 1</a>?(5:30)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/2d-transforms-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">2D Transforms: Part 2</a>?(5:25)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/3d-transforms-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">3D Transforms: Part 1</a>?(5:58)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/3d-transforms-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">3D Transforms: Part 2</a>?(6:04)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/animations-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Animations: Part 1</a>?(7:46)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/animations-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Animations: Part 2</a>?(7:34)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/project-part-1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Project: Part 1</a>?(6:45)</li>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/animation/project-part-2" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Project: Part 2</a>?(6:32)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Typography</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://membership.thinkvitamin.com/library/css3/typography/text-shadows" 